reviews.review_text: 1st show Grew up in Iowa City and happened to get called to work there. Got on the bus that night. This was the last and only show I could walk anywhere and stop to listen, students were away on the interim. Even though there were sound problems was a great show. Absolutely blew my mind! After awhile people on floor just put their chairs away in a pile on edge and started dancing. And a double encore! Thanks for the soundboard, I've had to make due with about 4th gen. audience tape all these years. Went on to see about 30 more shows but this one still stands out. Good little gem to check out.
